## 2. API Endpoints

### 🔐 Authentication
| Method | Endpoint | Description |
| :--- | :--- | :--- |
| `POST` | `/api/auth/register/customer/` | Register customer |
| `POST` | `/api/auth/register/seller/` | Register seller (with shop details) |
| `POST` | `/api/auth/login/` | Log in and get JWT tokens |
| `GET` | `/api/auth/profile/` | Fetch/update profiles |
| `PUT` | `/api/auth/seller/settings/` | Update shop address, location coords, and business hours |
| `POST` | `/api/auth/upload/` | Utility endpoint to upload profile pictures or banner media |

### 🛍️ Shops, Categories & Products
| Method | Endpoint | Description |
| :--- | :--- | :--- |
| `GET` | `/api/core/shops/` | List shops, support geospatial search (`?latitude=X&longitude=Y`) |
| `GET` | `/api/core/categories/` | List category trees with dynamic product counts |
| `GET` | `/api/core/products/` | Filter products by category, shop, and text search |
| `POST` | `/api/core/products/` | Create a product listing (Seller only) |
| `GET` | `/api/core/banners/` | Retrieve active banners/videos matching scheduled date/time |

### 🛒 Cart & Bills Management (In-Store Flow)
| Method | Endpoint | Description |
| :--- | :--- | :--- |
| `GET`/`POST`/`DELETE` | `/api/operations/cart/` | Manage customer cart items (supports guest mode via `guest_cart_id`) |
| `POST` | `/api/operations/checkout/` | Checkout and generate a Bill with status `Billed` |
| `GET` | `/api/operations/bills/customer/` | Customer bill list (purchase history) |
| `GET` | `/api/operations/bills/seller/` | Seller bills dashboard |
| `PUT` | `/api/operations/bills/<bill_id>/` | Update bill status (`Billed` -> `Paid` or `Cancelled`) |
| `GET` | `/api/operations/bills/<bill_id>/download/` | Download a clean, formatted PDF invoice |

### 📊 Excel Bulk Operations & Logs
| Method | Endpoint | Description |
| :--- | :--- | :--- |
| `POST` | `/api/operations/products/import/` | Upload excel sheet (`.xlsx`) to bulk import products |
| `GET` | `/api/operations/products/export/` | Export bills or products database to Excel/CSV |
| `GET` | `/api/operations/products/import/history/` | View Excel import log history and errors |

### 🎯 Recommendations (Upsell & Cross-sell)
| Method | Endpoint | Description |
| :--- | :--- | :--- |
| `POST` | `/api/marketing/recommendations/configure/` | Link source product to other items (Seller only) |
| `GET` | `/api/marketing/recommendations/<product_id>/` | Fetch linked cross-sell and upsell products |

