## 4. How to Start and Run the Server

To launch the Django development server on your machine, run:
```bash
# Navigate to project directory
cd winkart_backend

# Run Django server
..\venv\Scripts\python manage.py runserver 127.0.0.1:8000
```
The MongoDB client connects automatically to the local MongoDB service running on port `27017`.
